name: Kelly Moore Paints
overview:
Kelly-Moore Paint Company, Inc., a paint company, manufactures and sells paint products to painting professionals in the United States. It offers architectural paints and industrial products; E coat; and clear finishes, such as wood stains, clear finishes, ultra solids, water clear, precatalyzed lacquer, pigmented lacquers, conversion varnish, and CAB lacquers. The company also provides industrial maintenance coatings and products; and specialty products, including elastomeric coatings, textured paint, dry fogs, mill whites, and field striping paints. In addition, Kelly-Moore Paint Company offers sundries, which include abrasives, brushes and roller covers, caulking, clean-up, masking products, rollers, specialty paints and primers, and sprayers. The company offers its products for use in applications, such as new construction woodwork, furniture and cabinet manufacturing, commercial fixtures, and home decorating products. Kelly-Moore Paint Company provides its products through retail stores. It has manufacturing facilities in Seattle, Washington; and Hurst, Texas.

The company was founded in 1946 and is based in San Carlos, California.
